Package: wijayatunga
Type: Package
Title: Calculates Wijayatunga Coefficient
Version: 0.1.0
Year: 2021, January
Author: Vithor Rosa Franco <vithorfranco@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Vithor Rosa Franco <vithorfranco@gmail.com>
Description: This package is used to calculate the dependence measure proposed by
             Wijayatunga (2016), which generalizes Pearson's product-moment correlation
             to measure non-linear dependence between categorical variables.
             A function for a permutation test to get p-values are also provided.
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports: copula (>= 0.999-20),
         combinat (>= 0.0-8),
         infotheo (>= 1.2.0)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/vthorrf/wijayatunga
